\alpha q_N - p_N
\alpha q_{N-1} - p_{N-1}
|\alpha q - p| = |x (\alpha q_N - p_N) + y (\alpha q_{N-1} - p_{N-1})| = |x| |\alpha q_N - p_N| + |y| |\alpha q_{N-1} - p_{N-1}|
y=\alpha x
|\alpha q-p|=q|\alpha-\frac{p}{q}|
